<p>All audiovisual material, trademarks or any item subject to intellectual property contained in this website is owned by &#39;Hotel Nacional de Cuba&#39; or has sufficient rights to use. Reproduction of material mentioned is only permitted if it is for personal use only, forbids any modification, copying, hiring, lending, transmission and unauthorized disclosure.</p>

